# Agent Context

This file is loaded automatically by umabot every time it starts.
Edit it to give the assistant a persona, standing instructions, personal facts,
or any domain knowledge it should always have.

The content here is injected into every agent's system prompt — it applies to
all requests, all connectors, and all spawned sub-agents.

---

